I thought you would be interested in the weather forecast for the Wedding . The data includes max temp , max temp deviation from normal ( ie if max is 88 and normal max is 86 max temp deviation is +2) , min temp , min temp deviation from normal and percent of precipitation . So far things are looking good . We are getting a cold front this weekend ( hitting Texas on Monday ) and looks like things should be beautiful for next weekend . I wouldn't be that worried about the rain either - the reason the POP is so high right now is tropical moisture in the Gulf of Mexico and that will blow through this weekend . After that the tropics settle down and it is much less likely to get tropical moisture . City Forecast Date Max Temp Max Temp Deviation Min Temp Min Temp Deviation POP ( % )
